attributionInfo.brokerName: REAL ESTATE SERVICES OF PALM COAST
Berkshire Hathaway Homeservices Florida Network Realty

data.description: Upon entering this beautiful, 3/2/2 concrete block home, built in 2021, you will notice the perfect neutral color palette.  Granite throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, and an easy-to-maintain faux-wood vinyl, flooring, and spotless carpeting in bedrooms.   This is an open & pet-free home, allowing your pet to know they are now home.   No garage laundry in this adorable home, but features an interior laundry closet with wire shelving for your convenience.  As an added bonus, the home also includes both washer, dryer, and refrigerator, which means no added expenses for your customers.   Buyers will appreciate the potential insurance savings with a newer home. You will notice a vaulted kitchen/living area ceiling, creating the feel of a home bigger than the cozy 1200+ sqft the home boasts.   This would be the perfect starter home for a family, or for those looking to downsize, in this non-HOA community.   The central location of this property is close to schools, Rte 1, &  I 95, which provide plenty of shopping options, grocery stores, and City Hall approximately 2.2 miles from the home.  For all the beach lovers, enjoy an approximate 7 Mile drive or a bike ride, to Flagler Beach. Palm Coast is a popular NE Florida destination for nature lovers, and outdoor enthusiasts alike.   Water lovers will enjoy the miles of canals and Intracoastal waterway ideal for fishing,  boating, and drop-in spots for kayaking and paddle boarding.   Miles of the city trail system features walking and biking trails, which cover a huge part of the city. Many parks abound, and Palm Coast is building a brand new state-of-the-art, tennis center, featuring courts for the ever-popular pickleball sport that will be completed in a matter of months.  Centrally and strategically located in Northeast Florida. Palm Coast is approximately one hour N  to Jacksonville & one hour S to Orlando.  This is the one you’ve been waiting for! It’s priced to sell quickly.  Set up your private showing with your qualified buyers today.
